Description.Text: A good hotel with easy links to Moscow centre. 12/08 SC
The hotel is located in a quiet residential area north of Moscow's centre, within walking distance from metro station Petrovsko-Razumovskaya.
The rooms vary in size, but are generally medium to large. The rooms are furnished with wooden furniture and pastel colors. Bathrooms, with either bath or shower, are in good condition.
The hotel has the same traditional facade as the surrounding residential estates. The entrance of the hotel is somewhat hidden, but still easy to find.
The restaurant is open for breakfast in the morning. During the day Russian specialities are being served.
The lobby is small. There is a seating area opposite the small reception desk. There is also a small ticket office for train and bus tickets.
